headline: International Paper CEO to Speak at Jefferies 2025 Industrials Conference
summary: International Paper Chief Executive Officer Andy Silvernail will speak at Jefferies 2025 Industrials Conference on September 4, 2025. The presentation is scheduled to begin at 8:10 a.m. Eastern Daylight Time and will be followed by a question-and-answer session.
